    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The sol-diers stand-ing guard at Thy tomb, O my Sav-iour, be-came as dead on see-ing the light-ning-like An-gel who preached to the wom--en of Thine a-ris-ing, O Ho--ly Lord. Thee we glo--ri-fy, Who hast a-bol-ished cor-rup-tion; Thee do we__ a-dore, Who from the grave hast a-ris-en and Who a-lone art our God."
